{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Vercel Labs just dropped a new programming language.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ccedd6942d267a5dc17c1b5ca9744b01c72c7a2f69896d7cfe3502bbc67ddd16",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "It is called Zero. And it is built for agents, not humans.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6d4a867e990f9934533e502bac31a492f96daf647768f2c79f0b4400d3b27011",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 8
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Chris Tate posted this on May sixteenth.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5e290aba0a77cd63dac154eee9430de3fc9053f5fdee6d7dcaca68d4592bbf54",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 20
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "By the next morning, the repo had over nine hundred stars.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3cd9b8b5aac6bdd9ded473421349fa51fcbc238ebdc4ac8f2212fe1bcbf169c2",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "The tagline. The programming language for agents.",
      "checksum": "sha256:887f4e1bb04e9f5413d612cb16c34d5a73efe73bdd7a860f98b946b5d8d070bb",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 38
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "A systems language for small native tools, explicit effects, predictable memory, and structured compiler output.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f218d6ce9b816f9a654b7ccf08e94d0406c1062c2707f5afa035f5e9fe9f8d29",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 6.501587301587302,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 45
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Here is what a hello world looks like. Notice the file extension.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0c0f81f713a32d161f9e179ee6a02ab40fe2a60f4f86ca6dd584413b760e38e1",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.040272108843538,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 60
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Dot zero. Numeric zero. Inside main, you receive a World capability.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5e8500c5d19d1a4c6472b0967eaf249879892ea2b82416e8e9f53931fa86f4c9",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 4.73687074829932,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "If you want to write to standard output, you have to accept that World.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9067da5c2a37ed3842727e4bfe5661b8d0408dba0a413704a2c3885674dbb852",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 83
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "The function declares raises, meaning it can fail.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1cb64d6b118a90ec1e266e83caf06bd76a591aa6e9c0ddccec9dabd70046789a",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 97
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "And every side effect is prefixed with check, so the compiler can see exactly where you touched the outside.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7ff7523a19efb9452f680161d67cb17d857c1a78ca4c6f26c4cc09ddd03521a9",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 5.990748299319728,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 105
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Now look at this build line from the announcement.",
      "checksum": "sha256:68cb8c97b031114afc7cdf2242bdad7c19386fa0a288b9ccbc5dc07085ea5efd",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 124
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Sixteen kilobytes. One millisecond. That is the entire hello binary.",
      "checksum": "sha256:7cbb2dd3ed1a237e2682902ba7fa046fdd6736bdcdf369948b477e18dc8f6cf0",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 4.2260317460317465,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 133
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Statically linked. No runtime. Almost every command can emit jay-son.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ff8be0bdada85fb88bb006d064a9aa7cd7bc89800c5b588b16965fe50f0d2e8c",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 143
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Zero check. Zero run. Zero graph. Zero size.",
      "checksum": "sha256:62da3aba8b229dbf344db655a8a38111b7bec08166ac74db0b3fc9fb7db5456b",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 2.7399546485260773,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 153
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "Zero routes. Zero doctor. All of them speak structured output.",
      "checksum": "sha256:441df6e6624708676f64316924280a5a038fdd226714f46920b7c2f75266d2b7",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 161
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Because the audience is not a human reading a terminal.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e3a65c9ae18d1fc99dab9aed2a0e680deb35905eec3427d8a20e315ea5721c69",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 171
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "The audience is an agent reading a pipe.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d26035a2f236652536ba67064ba667abacc7c7d2261f246b4b65dcf91426632d",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.136235827664399,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 181
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Now the honest part. Zero is experimental.",
      "checksum": "sha256:33b9000dce45780e2590de12920138f45977b1fe99a8f4bc11e337573480f377",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 189
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "The README says it directly. The language is not stable.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3b1ef361b42fee0ae84d3527c7569f068a869d84d5c4a6d25b991a7b053457cb",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 196
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "There is no public module system documented yet.",
      "checksum": "sha256:3ee587ed23ed4b83e6f79f2dac4a745490d00a6b02986ad84292182320865fd6",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 206
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "No published benchmarks. The example programs are all under fifty lines.",
      "checksum": "sha256:01f1a94392f213ee6e6ec7458dffc330ee29a2a87df90ec6326ae7cd6af701d7",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 4.08671201814059,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 214
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "And the compiler is a brand new C codebase with a self-hosted rewrite already in progress.",
      "checksum": "sha256:00c8e5fe7255dc06e189570df9d91a7929b899f86093cb457bde0f7a07f23c86",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 16,
      "words_offset": 225
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "So here is the real question. Is this a genuine new category?",
      "checksum": "sha256:e177846c56b65e7001a875e4d8e81b020ac864d7485f1d028101e80b45a3307e",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.2043537414965986,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 241
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "A systems language built from day zero for the way agents actually write code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cd007fbb93b6314f379aa3aefae66a468b43405a32493289fae50930547e1459",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 253
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "Or is it just Go with better error JSON in a Vercel hoodie.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6d4a3f3b1cba83f820f61b5dccef52610c806e6ac82d57af06860bf7d9f2d602",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Drop your verdict below. Real language, or hype with a dot-zero extension.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2b8eacf4ca2285106e69ff9084b1ee6bfc5c758d2fb23dae891cfa8956862895",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 4.272471655328798,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 280
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "I want to read your take.",
      "checksum": "sha256:29999791e6d52afe0e031ea63fad176cb3da677d916da8ea9418521dc5e873a4",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 1.3931972789115645,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 292
    }
  ]
}